    <h1>SEO <span class="mark">Audit</span> for Guildford and Surrey Businesses</h1>

    <p>An SEO audit is, at its core, an act of diagnosis, a systematic analysis of every factor that shapes your website's search engine performance, from server infrastructure and content quality through to local search presence and emerging AI visibility. For Guildford businesses competing within Surrey's high-value commercial landscape, an audit strips away assumptions and reveals, with forensic clarity, precisely why your site ranks where it does and what must change to shift those positions upward.</p>

    <div class="quick-answer">
