    </div>

    <div class="not-prose my-8 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4">
      <a href="/free-seo-audit-guildford/" class="cta-button">Request a free audit</a>
      <a href="#enquire" class="cta-link">Ask a question &rarr;</a>
    </div>
    <p class="cta-note">Free and without obligation. A reply within one working day.</p>

    <div class="reveal">
    <h2>What My SEO Audit Covers</h2>

    <p>A comprehensive SEO audit is not a tool-generated PDF. It is an expert-led investigation that examines your site through three distinct lenses: the search engine's, the user's, and your competitors'. I assess over 200 ranking factors across four categories, each weighted and prioritised by its impact on your specific business objectives. The difference between this and an automated report is the difference between a blood test and a consultation with a specialist.</p>

