    <div class="reveal">
    <h2>Local SEO Audit Components</h2>

    <p>For businesses serving Guildford and surrounding Surrey towns, local search visibility often drives the highest-value traffic. The local audit examines every factor that affects your visibility in Google's local pack and map results.</p>

    <h3>Google Business Profile</h3>

    <p>I audit your Google Business Profile for completeness, accuracy, category selection, photo quality, review management, and post activity. An optimised GBP is the single largest factor in local pack ranking, and I check that your primary and secondary categories accurately reflect your services and that your service area covers the correct geography.</p>

    <h3>Citation Consistency</h3>

    <p>Your business name, address, and phone number must be identical across every directory, social profile, and mention on the web. I audit your citations across major UK directories (Yell, Thomson Local, Yelp, FreeIndex, Cylex) and industry-specific platforms, since inconsistencies confuse Google and suppress local rankings.</p>

    <h3>Local Content and Landing Pages</h3>

    <p>I evaluate whether your site has sufficient local content to demonstrate genuine relevance to Guildford and surrounding areas. This includes location-specific service pages, local case studies, area guides, and geo-modified keyword targeting. Thin location pages that differ only by town name are flagged as a risk.</p>

    <h3>Review Profile</h3>

    <p>I analyse your review volume, recency, rating distribution, and response rate across Google and relevant platforms. Review signals influence local rankings directly, and I benchmark your profile against local competitors to identify gaps in your review acquisition approach.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="reveal">
    <h2>AI Search Readiness Audit</h2>

    <p>Search is changing. ChatGPT, Perplexity, Google AI Overviews, and Microsoft Copilot now answer queries directly, often citing sources. If your site is not structured for AI extraction, you lose visibility in these channels entirely.</p>

    <p>My AI search readiness audit examines:</p>

    <ul>
      <li>Whether your content appears in AI-generated answers for your target queries.</li>
      <li>Content structure and formatting that AI systems can extract and cite.</li>
      <li>Presence of an llms.txt file and AI-friendly metadata.</li>
      <li>Entity markup that helps AI systems understand your business and expertise.</li>
      <li>Citation patterns in competitor AI mentions.</li>
    </ul>

    <p>This is a newer audit component that most SEO agencies do not yet offer. For Guildford technology companies and <strong>University of Surrey</strong> spinouts competing in innovation-driven markets, AI search visibility is already a meaningful competitive advantage. My <a href="/ai-search-optimisation-guildford/">AI search optimisation service</a> covers ongoing implementation.</p>
    </div>

