    <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-3">
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>How long does an SEO audit take?</summary>
        <p>A comprehensive SEO audit for a Guildford business takes five to ten working days depending on site size. A 50-page professional services site typically takes around five days, while e-commerce or property listing sites with thousands of pages require up to ten days for thorough analysis.</p>
